```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph Supabase[Supabase]
        DB[(PostgreSQL DB)]
        API[(PostgREST API)]
        Auth[(GoTrue Auth)]
        Realtime[(Realtime WS)]
        Storage[(Storage Bucket)]
        Edge[(Edge Functions)]
    end
    subgraph Directus[Directus CMS]
        DirectusAPI[(Directus API)]
    end
    subgraph Cloudinary[Cloudinary]
        Cloud[(Media CDN)]
    end
    subgraph Analytics[Analytics]
        PostHog[(PostHog)]
        Firebase[(Firebase Analytics)]
    end
    %% Connections
    DirectusAPI -->|Sync migrations| DB
    Edge -->|Upload URL| Cloud
    Cloud -->|Media URLs| DB
    DB --> API
    Auth --> API
    Realtime --> API
    Storage --> API
    Edge --> API
    API -->|Events| Realtime
    API -->|Analytics calls| PostHog
    API -->|Analytics calls| Firebase
```
